 Write the codes for the patterns

1.

	*
	**
	***
	****

code :	

public class MyClass {
    public static void main(String args[]) {
        int n=5;
        for(int i=0;i<5;i++){
            for(int j=0;j<i;j++){
                System.out.print("*");    
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
